OL,3,CNHS hospitals plagued by rats,
OL,4,Ccockroaches and silverfish, staff say
OL,6,FSilverfish are metallic, silvery bugs
OL,7,Fthat thrive in damp conditions while
OL,8,Fcockroaches can carry diseases and
OL,9,Fillnesses such as gastroenteritis,
OL,10,Fdiarrhoea, typhoid and salmonella.
OL,12,FRats carry several diseases such as
OL,13,Fleptospirosis (Weil's disease), which
OL,14,Fis spread in their urine.
OL,16,FThe new survey also found 17% of staff
OL,17,Fdo not think their building is safe.
