OL,6,FMore than half reported seeing buckets
OL,7,Fcatching leaking water in their
OL,8,Fworkplace buildings in the past year
OL,9,Fwhile almost a quarter witnessed
OL,10,Fsewage leaks.
OL,12,FSome 28% said public toilets in their
OL,13,Fhospitals have been out of order for
OL,14,Fextended periods while 30% reported
OL,15,Fbroken staff toilets.
OL,17,FOne member of staff working in the
OL,18,Fnorth-west of England reported rodent
OL,19,Fbait boxes being used all over his
OL,20,Fhospital and a leaking waste pipe
OL,21,Fwhich had resulted in a foul odour.
