OL,6,FHelga Pile, Unison head of health,
OL,7,Fsaid: "This survey paints a worrying
OL,8,Fpicture of an NHS system that's
OL,9,Ffalling apart at the seams and in need
OL,10,Fof a serious overhaul.
OL,12,F"No one should be dodging rats,
OL,13,Fstepping over sewage or watching out
OL,14,Ffor falling ceiling tiles in NHS
OL,15,Fbuildings.
OL,17,F"The last thing patients or staff want
OL,18,Fis vermin, cockroaches and other
OL,19,Funpleasant things roaming the wards.
OL,20,FDisease-carrying pests can put
OL,21,Fpeople's health at risk.
